  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a libgdata</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libgdata</application> package is a GLib-based library for
accessing online service APIs using the GData protocol, most notably,
Google's services. It provides APIs to access the common Google services and
has full asynchronous support.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

